OL,3,CMurder investigation launched 35 years
OL,4,Cafter the death of a 92-year-old man
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched 35 years after the death of a
OL,8,F92-year-old man.
OL,10,FBentley Mathias, 92, died on 19th
OL,11,FNovember 1991 in Morriston Hospital,
OL,12,Fwith the cause of death recorded as a
OL,13,Fbrain haemorrhage.
OL,15,FHis death was not treated as
OL,16,Fsuspicious at the time but police say
OL,17,Fnew potential evidence has come to
OL,18,Flight and are now treating the
OL,19,Fincident as a murder enquiry.
