OL,3,CMurder investigation launched 35 years
OL,4,Cafter the death of a 92-year-old man
OL,6,FDyfed Powys Police says it arrested a
OL,7,F67-year-old man from the Llandewi
OL,8,FVelfrey area of Pembrokeshire on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder on Wednesday (22
OL,10,FJuly).
OL,12,FHe has been bailed while police
OL,13,Fcontinue with their enquiries. Police
OL,14,Fsay they are not looking for anyone
OL,15,Felse in relation to this matter, and
OL,16,Fthe investigation is ongoing.
